metadata:
  section_id: 8
  section_name: رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا سرمہ لگانا
  hadith_first: 49
  hadith_last: 53

hadiths[5]{hadithnumber,text,grades,reference,international_number,narrator_chain,chapter_intro}:
49,"'Abdullah ibn Muhammad ibn 'Uqail also informed us: ""I saw the hair of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) dyed in the presence of Anas ibn Malik.""",,,49,"Hammad said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا سرمہ لگانا
50,"""Color the edges of the eyelids with antimony [ithmid], for it clears the vision and makes the eyelashes grow!” He also maintained that the Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) had a kohl jar from which he used to apply kohl to his eyelashes every night, three times in this [eye],and three times in that.",,,50,"Ibn 'Abbas reported that the Prophet said (Allah bless him and give him peace):",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا سرمہ لگانا
51,"“Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) used to color the edges of his eyelids with antimony before going to sleep, three times in each eye.\nYazid ibn Harun also said in his tradition: “The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) had a kohl jar from which he used to apply kohl to his eyelashes before going to sleep, three times in each eye.”",,,51,"Ibn 'Abbas said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا سرمہ لگانا
52,"""Allah’s Messenger said (Allah bless him and give him peace): “You must apply antimony before going to sleep, for it clears the vision and makes the eyelashes grow.”",,,52,"Jabir (i.e. Ibn Abdillah) said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا سرمہ لگانا
53,"""Allah’s Messenger said (Allah bless him and give him peace): 'The best of your eye salves is antimony, for it clears the vision and makes the eyelashes grow.'”",,,53,"Ibn ""Abbas said:",رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا سرمہ لگانا
